__pycache__/
*.pyc

# This repo is the usage-counts destination: skill-usage.json is tracked here on
# purpose, as metadata about the skills it counts. It is committed to a PUBLIC
# repo by deliberate choice — see README. Only the lock and the atomic-write
# temp files stay ignored; they are transient and machine-local.
.skill-usage.lock
.skill-usage-*.tmp
